{"tid":2507963,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"PSG向美斯開出一份2+1合約","createTime":"2021-04-28T11:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T11:40:56.000Z","uid":54712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76aee8187c2f547a69170177a9d71d042a80f762","tid":2507963,"uid":54712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"尼馬自爆同PSG續約 隨時搶埋美斯拍住上 <br />\n<br />\n尼馬同巴黎聖日耳門（PSG）嘅合約喺明年6月到期，過去一直有傳呢位巴西球星會離開，雖然目前雙方仍未續約，但尼馬自爆已經傾得七七八八，續約接近完成。<br />\n<br />\nPSG已經打入歐聯四強，佢哋上年攞亞軍，今年當然要向冠軍進發，而尼馬都希望可以成功捧盃，如果真係成功同PSG續約，相信球迷會好開心。另方面，有消息指PSG已經向巴塞隆拿出手搶阿根廷球王美斯，成功的話又可以同尼馬拍住上。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>據《世界體育報》頭條報道，PSG已向美斯開出一份2+1嘅合約，其中薪金待遇都係巴塞無得揮，而且仲用埋PSG嘅球隊成績嚟誘惑美斯，畢竟聖日耳門上屆殺入歐聯決賽，今屆又已躋身四強，絕對「配」得起美斯。</strong><br />\n美斯同巴塞嘅合約到今夏結束，但美斯家陣只想專注一件事，就係幫巴塞爭西甲冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210428/bkn-20210428140549059-0428_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20210428%2Fbkn-20210428140549059-0428_00882_001.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0uQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=823d9e53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210428/bkn-20210428140549059-0428_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4d5de576718e801afbca7871fa2b69d44528864c","tid":2507963,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"one club man???"},{"pid":"bcb4e7d3bd89578eec10cdde3ce8043305c12160","tid":2507963,"uid":217861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"美斯要為巴塞踢歐超聯<br />\n忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980f0503f56f7b87bc39cbdedc9519a88925bfa0","tid":2507963,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"轉會: 又話one club man?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔轉會: 溫室小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己揀個罪狀"},{"pid":"0c9b55ea8c36ff98673dd5ceefdc309b1838ce56","tid":2507963,"uid":54712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"全世界最早確認尼馬轉會和美斯渴望離隊的記者Marcelo Bechler，在當地時間本周二透露，PSG向美斯提供了一份2+1的合約。<br />\n<br />\n根據Bechler的說法，巴黎方面認為單純從經濟上來看，這份報價是無敵的。巴塞目前處於嚴重的經濟危機中，巴黎希望在錢上打動美斯。"},{"pid":"2fc8113c477cf7a6dd0cada18bea48795701d707","tid":2507963,"uid":90515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"980f0503f56f7b87bc39cbdedc9519a88925bfa0","tid":2507963,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"轉會: 又話one club man?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔轉會: 溫室小花<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己揀個罪狀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"我地朗迷又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0090a8ddd9e31596da7b843380bdfee19e3dac","tid":2507963,"uid":54712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"真係過左去SO9會唔會好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93cf29b75135a497f2b0782d43db864d8062d146","tid":2507963,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:33:57.000Z","msg":"毒撚最怕走出comfort zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46f11cf538ca635b58dbfad3f3fd735c96b359a","tid":2507963,"uid":54137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"美欺都走埋 邊個仲會睇西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3c9011d4e9928c3fbf5c980ed2b53a21d038e0","tid":2507963,"uid":54712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46f11cf538ca635b58dbfad3f3fd735c96b359a","tid":2507963,"uid":54137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"美欺都走埋 邊個仲會睇西甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"有賓周馬<br />\n牙朗走左之後上哂身"},{"pid":"a8dfc64ec72f6d51c7e8ec3633168d6d3fb977d6","tid":2507963,"uid":34163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"球星隊係好睇<br />\n但係更加想睇各自係唔同隊互相對抗<br />\n不過巴塞真係冇咩留底既價值"}]}